If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : skillsupport@atlanticenergyco.com
Amazon Alexa and the Atlantic Energy Connect home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Atlantic Energy Connect products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Atlantic Energy" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register your Atlantic Energy account in our "Atlantic Energy" app;
(3). You need to have some Atlantic Energy devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Atlantic Energy app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Atlantic Energy Connect " skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Atlantic Energy Connect " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Atlantic Energy Connect ", and you'll be navigated to Atlantic Energy login page;
(9). Input your Atlantic Energy account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
“Alexa, turn on bedroom air conditioner"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb....
